1. To install the core ldv tools use:
     prefix=/path/to/your/installation/directory make install
2. To install the ldv manager use:
     prefix=/path/to/your/installation/directory make install-srv
3. To install the statistics server use:
     prefix=/path/to/your/installation/directory make install-stats-server
4. To install tests use:
     prefix=/path/to/your/installation/directory make install-test
5. To install all use:
     prefix=/path/to/your/installation/directory make install-all

Note, that '3' and '5' most likely require root privelegies and additional
setup. See 'stats-visualizer/README' for details. 
